  "detailed_description": "One of the twin turtles is trying to save his brother which was abducted by a monster. He decided to go after the monster via the portal system. When he exits from the portal system, things were different. He finds some surprising facts to move next.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why Turtle vs. Portal?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379450/extras/948e42db4ccb6aef17346c212a9ebb1b.poster.avif?t=1622634799\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379450/extras/948e42db4ccb6aef17346c212a9ebb1b.webm?t=1622634799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379450/extras/948e42db4ccb6aef17346c212a9ebb1b.mp4?t=1622634799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turtle vs. Portal that everyone, of all ages, can ENJOY!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379450/extras/256473d55294de702029c2b577c10d95.avif?t=1622634799\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The worlds had different types of themes and different sets of levels, and branching paths to discover.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379450/extras/46acabd851afa722cc266383c7e69850.avif?t=1622634799\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Which began a platformer soon unravels into a portal system adventure full of the puzzle, surprises, thrill, and more.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story based game play and it support 12 languages (everything except audio).</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>72 unique levels (8 worlds x 9 levels).</li></u